Bitmap Transformer:
    Usage: node index.js <flags> <inputfile> <outputfile>

        Description: Transforms the input file and writes it as the output file.

        Inputfile:
        Any uncompressed 2/4/8/24/32-bit bitmap

        Outputfile:
        The format is unchanged.  If the file exists, it will be overwritten.

        Flags
        --help	View this help page
        --list	View a list of transform options
